  <summary>2/3/2005--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the amortization, over a 24-month period, of: (1) delay rental payments for the development of oil or gas wells in the United States; and (2) geological and geophysical expenses incurred in the exploration for, or development of, oil or gas in the United States.</summary>
